description: This header file defines the prototypes for exported functions related to the CCSP CWMP Connection Object, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions. It serves as an interface for other components to interact with the CCSP CWMP ACS connection object.

methods.name: CcspCwmpCreateAcsConnection
methods.description: Creates an ACS connection handle with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: CcspCwmpAcscoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the CCSP CWMP ACS connection object.

methods.name: CcspCwmpAcscoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleanup the specified ACS connection object.

methods.name: CcspCwmpAcscoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls required objects in the ACS connection object.
